Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.32,0:03:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<font size=28 color=#00d8f8>三十年以来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.49,0:03:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<font size=28 color=#00d8f8>强大的无线电
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.79,0:03:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<font size=28 color=#00d8f8>望远镜扫射天空
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.29,0:03:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<font size=28 color=#00d8f8>寻找异外文化的讯号
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.00,0:03:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<font size=28 color=#00d8f8>这个计划名为S.E.T.I.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.00,0:03:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<font size=28 color=#00d8f8>就是探索地球之外的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.34,0:03:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<font size=28 color=#00d8f8>美国政府实验室 犹他州达格韦市
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.22,0:05:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<font size=28 color=#00d8f8>氛化物毒气体
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.94,0:05:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起\N{\rENG}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.27,0:05:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起？\N{\rENG}I'm sorry?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.62,0:06:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她逃出来了\N{\rENG}Sir, she's breaking out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.53,0:06:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们去找什么？\N{\rENG}What are we looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.21,0:07:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她跳过围栏！\N{\rENG}She jumped over the fence!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.41,0:08:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她逃离时有两班火车．驶经这里\N{\rENG}A couple of trains came through here about the time she escaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.41,0:08:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那短时间内 她能走这么远？\N{\rENG}Do you think she could have gotten this far in that time?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.66,0:08:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她有这么快吗？\N{\rENG}Is she that fast?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.33,0:08:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她就是这么快\N{\rENG}She is that fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.79,0:09:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有这个\N{\rENG}And this too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.26,0:09:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 三元一角 - 三元一角？\N{\rENG}- $3. 10. - Three dollars and ten cents?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.47,0:09:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你的零钱 - 谢谢\N{\rENG}- Your change. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.64,0:09:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么可帮你吗？\N{\rENG}Can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.35,0:09:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总共十七元九毛五\N{\rENG}The total is $ 17.95.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.32,0:09:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的卡\N{\rENG}Here's your card.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.82,0:09:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想买那些吗？\N{\rENG}Are you gonna buy those?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.33,0:09:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,旅途愉快\N{\rENG}Have a nice trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.67,0:10:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是褐色斜纹的帆布袋 有见过吗？\N{\rENG}It's brown tweed bag, like a duffel. Do you see it anywhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.47,0:10:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 先生，不在这里  - 服务生说是放在手推车上的\N{\rENG}- Sir, it's not here. - The porter said he put it on the cart.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.18,0:10:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是手推车 不过没有帆布袋\N{\rENG}This is the cart. There's no bag here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.37,0:10:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,政府当局说 这是最大型的地震\N{\rENG}Government authorities said it was the largest earthquake to strike...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.13,0:10:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他骑着油脂闪电\N{\rENG}He's riding Greased Lightning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.21,0:10:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是金凯德\N{\rENG}That was Shorty Kincaid.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.59,0:10:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请享受风景\N{\rENG}Enjoy the view.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.79,0:11:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思\N{\rENG}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.27,0:11:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们不应给别人看到\N{\rENG}We shouldn't be seen together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.02,0:11:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,父亲死去不久 你认为阿伦会怀疑吗？\N{\rENG}Father hasn't been dead long. Do you think Arlen suspects?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.77,0:11:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，我们也不是 立刻在一起的\N{\rENG}No. It's not too soon for us to be together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.78,0:11:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请拿出车票\N{\rENG}Tickets.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.45,0:11:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你独自旅行吗？\N{\rENG}Are you traveling by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.95,0:11:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你十二岁？\N{\rENG}You're 12?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.46,0:11:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人在洛杉矶接你吗？\N{\rENG}Someone meeting you in Los Angeles?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.88,0:11:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当你十一岁吧 那么你只须付半价\N{\rENG}We'll say you're 11. Then you only pay half price.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.32,0:12:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我们的小女孩做的？\N{\rENG}Our little girl did this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.32,0:12:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她不是小女孩\N{\rENG}She's not a little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.15,0:12:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伤口发现的DNA类别和组织 都证实是属于她的\N{\rENG}DNA typing and material found in those wounds proves it was her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.91,0:12:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她可到任何地方，芝加哥 拉斯维加斯、洛杉矶\N{\rENG}She could be anywhere. Chicago, Las Vegas, Los Angeles, anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.08,0:12:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要截停火车\N{\rENG}We should stop the trains.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.58,0:12:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,铁路人员和警方查问时 我们怎么回答？\N{\rENG}And have the railroad and police ask questions we can't answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.34,0:12:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们会派人在这些路线上的 每个站守候\N{\rENG}We'll put key personnel at every stop along these lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.01,0:12:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要派一个队伍追踪她\N{\rENG}I want a team to track her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.26,0:12:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把她搜寻回来\N{\rENG}Hunt her down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.51,0:12:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 早安，吉尔  - 你好\N{\rENG}- Good morning, Jill. - Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.51,0:12:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 麻烦你照顾我的猫  - 我们会好好照顾他\N{\rENG}- Thanks for taking care of my cat. - We'll take good care of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.35,0:12:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很快就会回来\N{\rENG}I won't be gone very long.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.27,0:12:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保重\N{\rENG}Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.48,0:12:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见\N{\rENG}Bye-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.65,0:13:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的工作还不顺利吗？\N{\rENG}Are you still having problems with the people at work?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.69,0:13:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们都说我…\N{\rENG}They point their finger at me saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.53,0:13:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是怪人，很古怪\N{\rENG}I'm the weird one, I'm the strange one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.62,0:13:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？因为我有感觉？\N{\rENG}Why? Because I have feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.79,0:13:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因我有感应？\N{\rENG}Because I feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.62,0:13:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,门外有人\N{\rENG}There's someone at the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.29,0:13:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不打算应门 任何人也可以稍后再来\N{\rENG}I won't answer that. Whoever it is can come back at the end of the hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.47,0:13:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是找我的\N{\rENG}That's for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.55,0:13:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉打扰你们 我们需要你帮忙\N{\rENG}Sorry to interrupt. We need your help, Dan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.06,0:13:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道\N{\rENG}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.56,0:13:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得先离开了\N{\rENG}Gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.81,0:15:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,菲奇先生稍后就会来\N{\rENG}Mr. Fitch will be with you all in just a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.69,0:15:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是了…\N{\rENG}Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.15,0:15:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,似乎我们都是为了 相同原因而来\N{\rENG}I guess we all must be here for the same reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.57,0:15:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不论那是什么原因\N{\rENG}whatever that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.83,0:15:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是丹史密森\N{\rENG}I'm Dan Smithson...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.83,0:16:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道我为何会来\N{\rENG}and I don't know why I'm here either.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.62,0:16:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过他们说需要我，而且这是 重要事情，所以我才来\N{\rENG}But they said they needed me and it was important, so I came.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.79,0:16:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你做什么工作的？\N{\rENG}What do you do, Dan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.63,0:16:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是心灵感应者\N{\rENG}I'm an empath.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.22,0:16:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有时他让我看别人做的可怕事情\N{\rENG}Sometimes they show me awful things people have done.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.89,0:16:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我尝试告诉他们为何会这样做\N{\rENG}I try to tell them why they did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.89,0:16:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有什么资格这样做？\N{\rENG}What qualifies you for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.81,0:16:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我对事物有深切感受 就是这样\N{\rENG}I feel things deeply, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.90,0:16:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我现在有什么感受？\N{\rENG}What am I feeling now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.91,0:16:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你相信没什么会影响你\N{\rENG}You wanna believe that nothing affects you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.33,0:16:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你什么也不怕\N{\rENG}that you're not afraid of anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.42,0:16:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过你很好奇\N{\rENG}But you're curious...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.96,0:16:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像我们所有人一样\N{\rENG}just like the rest of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.17,0:16:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,史蒂文阿登，哈佛人类学系\N{\rENG}Stephen Arden. Harvard Anthropology Department.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.18,0:16:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,专门研究跨文化行为\N{\rENG}Expert at cross-cultural behavior.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.09,0:16:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罗拉贝克，分子生物学家\N{\rENG}Laura Baker. Hi. Molecular biologist.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.60,0:17:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你呢？你做什么的？\N{\rENG}And who are you, and what do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.02,0:17:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,普雷斯顿伦诺斯\N{\rENG}Preston Lennox.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.44,0:17:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我来到这里\N{\rENG}And if I'm here...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.36,0:17:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就证明有灾难发生\N{\rENG}the shit has hit the fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.11,0:17:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伦诺斯先生 你的专长在哪一方面？\N{\rENG}What exactly is your area of specialty, Mr. Lennox?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.70,0:17:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔会为政府解决问题\N{\rENG}I'm a freelance solution to our government's problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.37,0:17:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会是什么问题？\N{\rENG}What exactly might they be?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.04,0:17:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一些别人不爱提及的问题\N{\rENG}The kind people don't usually like to talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.08,0:17:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你追捕别人，是吧？\N{\rENG}You hunt people, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.68,0:17:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以这样说\N{\rENG}I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.06,0:17:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在吗？时候不早了 还看电视\N{\rENG}You in here? It's a little late for Tv.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.90,0:17:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在吗？\N{\rENG}You in here, honey?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.71,0:18:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安，我是萨维尔菲奇\N{\rENG}Good evening, I'm Xavier Fitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.54,0:18:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次行动由我负责\N{\rENG}I'm in charge of this operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.54,0:18:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坐靠近一点可以吗？\N{\rENG}Would you sit a little closer, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.56,0:19:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1974年11月\N{\rENG}In November of 1974...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.73,0:19:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S.E.T.I.的一个小组…\N{\rENG}a small group from S.E.T. I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.31,0:19:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S.E.T.I.就是 〝探索地球之外的生命〞计划\N{\rENG}S- E-T-I, Search for Extraterrestrial Intelligence...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.56,0:19:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,利用阿雷西沃的无线电天线\N{\rENG}used radio dishes at Arecibo
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.15,0:19:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向所有人发放一个讯息\N{\rENG}to send a message to whoever was listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.40,0:19:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们发放了250位元的讯息\N{\rENG}They sent a quarter of a kilobyte...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.32,0:19:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,包括人类DNA的构造\N{\rENG}including structure of human DNA...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.16,0:19:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们太阳系的图表\N{\rENG}a map of our solar system...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.41,0:19:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地球人口等有帮助的事实\N{\rENG}population of the Earth. Helpful facts like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.87,0:19:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1993年1月 阿雷西沃接收到一个讯息\N{\rENG}In January of 1993, Arecibo received a message back...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.25,0:19:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由外太空传送来的…\N{\rENG}from an extra terrestrial...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.22,0:19:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但来历不明\N{\rENG}unknown source.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.88,0:19:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真酷\N{\rENG}That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.39,0:19:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地球以外的智慧生物？\N{\rENG}Intelligent life beyond this planet?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.93,0:19:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对\N{\rENG}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.72,0:19:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讯息有两个\NThere were two communications.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.10,0:19:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一个讯息促使 我们发现到甲烷\N{\rENG}The first message turned out to be a superior catalyst for methane.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.90,0:19:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们现在有潜能…\N{\rENG}We now have the potential...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.36,0:19:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从这燃料制造无限的能源\N{\rENG}to produce infinite energy from this clean-burning fuel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.44,0:20:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这使我们相信 他们是友善的生物\N{\rENG}This convinced us we were dealing with a friendly intelligence.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.99,0:20:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第二个讯息 是一个DNA的新排列\N{\rENG}The second message turned out to be a new sequence of DNA...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.91,0:20:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并友善的指示 怎么与我们的DNA结合\N{\rENG}with friendly instructions on how to combine it with ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.08,0:20:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是技术上的数据 该由贝克博士解说\N{\rENG}Here's some technical data. Get feedback from Dr. Baker.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.33,0:20:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基本上\N{\rENG}Basically...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.63,0:20:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新组合的DNA排列次序\N{\rENG}the new combined DNA sequence...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.34,0:20:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被注进一百个…\N{\rENG}was injected into 100...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.34,0:20:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人类的卵细胞中\N{\rENG}human ova.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.39,0:20:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有七个…\N{\rENG}We got 7...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.64,0:20:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,产生分裂\N{\rENG}to divide.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.02,0:20:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四个逐渐停止了\N{\rENG}Four petered out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.98,0:20:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,两个储在液体氮气中\N{\rENG}Two were stored in liquid nitrogen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.65,0:20:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们让一个成长\N{\rENG}And we allowed one to grow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.65,0:20:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它的代号是〝西尔〞\N{\rENG}Its code name is "Sil."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.19,0:20:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是两小时后的形态\N{\rENG}That's after 2 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.32,0:20:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 天\N{\rENG}One day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.49,0:20:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,两天\N{\rENG}Two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.66,0:20:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 天啊  - 这成长过程真惊人\N{\rENG}- My God. - This growth is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.25,0:20:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 星期\N{\rENG}A week.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.29,0:20:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 是女孩子  - 对\N{\rENG}- It's a girl. - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.50,0:21:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们制造一个雌性 那么她就较温驯\N{\rENG}We decided to make it female so it would be more docile...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.71,0:21:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 和较易控制  - 温驯和容易受控？\N{\rENG}and controllable. - More docile and controllable, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.51,0:21:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们消息真不灵通\N{\rENG}Well, I guess you guys don't get out much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.68,0:21:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是她出生后一个月的状态\N{\rENG}That's her 1 month after she was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.43,0:21:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你把她关在那儿？\N{\rENG}So you kept her caged in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.23,0:21:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隔离她比较安全\N{\rENG}It was safer to keep her isolated.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.02,0:21:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她不喜欢这样\N{\rENG}She didn't like being locked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.48,0:21:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她不喜欢独自一人\N{\rENG}She didn't like being alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.40,0:21:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？\N{\rENG}Didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.95,0:21:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她在隐藏身体里的一些东西\N{\rENG}She's hiding something. Something inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.62,0:21:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说得没错\N{\rENG}You're right, Dan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.46,0:21:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是她三个月大的情形 留心看\N{\rENG}This is three months after she was born. Watch carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.54,0:21:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么？\N{\rENG}What the hell was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.71,0:21:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把录影带转回\N{\rENG}Back the tape up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.30,0:21:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看她双眼\N{\rENG}Watch her eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.39,0:21:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛急速跳动，她在做梦\N{\rENG}Rapid eye movement. She's dreaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.06,0:21:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 可怕的噩梦  - 是焦虑造成的反应\N{\rENG}- She's having horrible nightmares. - It's some kind of anxiety reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.90,0:22:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也感到忧虑\N{\rENG}Got me a little anxious.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.40,0:22:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也使研究队伍有点担忧\N{\rENG}It made the research team a little anxious too...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.90,0:22:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们决定中止实验\N{\rENG}so the decision was made to terminate the experiment...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.57,0:22:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,转而研究我们要应付什么\N{\rENG}to run more research to see what we were dealing with.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.24,0:22:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们打算毒死她？\N{\rENG}You were going to gas her?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.79,0:22:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是我们的决定\N{\rENG}That was the decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.25,0:22:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那使你很难受\N{\rENG}It makes you feel mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.34,0:22:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要杀死她你很难过，对吗？\N{\rENG}You feel mad that you had to kill her, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.09,0:22:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道\N{\rENG}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.76,0:22:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对\N{\rENG}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.65,0:22:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天在盐湖城附近的 一辆火车内发现一具尸体\N{\rENG}Yesterday the body of a transient was found in a boxcar near Salt Lake City.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.99,0:22:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,初步DNA测试所得的结论是\N{\rENG}Preliminary DNA tests conclude...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.65,0:22:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是被我们的西尔所杀的\N{\rENG}he was killed by our creation, by our Sil.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.07,0:22:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发现到其他尸体吗？\N{\rENG}Found any other bodies?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.74,0:22:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 还没  - 晚一点就会\N{\rENG}- Not yet. - You will.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.58,0:22:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是个掠食者\N{\rENG}She's a predator.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.33,0:22:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她双眼在前面\N{\rENG}Her eyes are in front...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.29,0:23:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她能够判断跟猎物的距离\N{\rENG}so she can judge the distance to her prey.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.46,0:23:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对\N{\rENG}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.75,0:23:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你从哪里学会的？\N{\rENG}Where'd you learn that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.71,0:23:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,探索频道播放的节目\N{\rENG}I saw it on the Discovery Channel.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.05,0:23:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也有看那节目\N{\rENG}I caught that show myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.76,0:23:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 伦诺斯先生  - 什么事？\N{\rENG}- Mr. Lennox. - Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.39,0:23:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们…\N{\rENG}As the...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.18,0:23:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都不是科学家 你们明白在发生什么事吗？\N{\rENG}non-scientist amongst us, are you clear about what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.94,0:23:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白\N{\rENG}I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.77,0:23:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你得到外太空的一个程式\N{\rENG}You created a monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.36,0:23:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以此制造了一个怪物\N{\rENG}with a formula you got from outer space.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.70,0:23:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她逃走了 你想我们追寻和杀死她\N{\rENG}The damn thing got away. Now you want us to hunt it down and kill it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.79,0:23:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不对？\N{\rENG}Now, is that pretty close?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.83,0:23:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以这样说\N{\rENG}I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.46,0:23:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不想我们\N{\rENG}You don't want us...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.96,0:23:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,活捉她和研究她吗？\N{\rENG}to capture her alive so that we can study her?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.38,0:23:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是一次纯寻找 和纯消灭的行动\N{\rENG}Laura, I think this is strictly a search and destroy operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.18,0:23:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向我求助的人 都想消灭他们的目标\N{\rENG}Nobody ever asked me to find anything they didn't want dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.81,0:23:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我为你难过\N{\rENG}I'm sorry for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.14,0:24:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊\N{\rENG}Yeah, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.19,0:24:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你\N{\rENG}Thank you, Dan.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.65,0:24:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我替她难过\N{\rENG}I'm sorry for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.86,0:24:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请注意\N{\rENG}May I have your attention, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.19,0:24:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎到洛杉矶来 这是沙漠之星的终站\N{\rENG}Welcome to Los Angeles. This is the terminal stop for the Desert Star.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.66,0:24:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请所有乘客离开\N{\rENG}All passengers please disembark.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.71,0:24:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<font size=28 color=#00d8f8>洛杉矶
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.95,0:25:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有坏事发生了\N{\rENG}Something bad happened here.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.28,0:25:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 天啊 - 她的喉给压碎了\N{\rENG}- No shit. - Crushed her larynx.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.28,0:25:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她很怕\N{\rENG}She was afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.20,0:25:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她害怕、惊慌\N{\rENG}She's scared, frightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.79,0:25:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还很饿，她吃了很多\N{\rENG}Hungry too. She's been eating like a horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.21,0:25:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她显然不是在节食\N{\rENG}Our girl is definitely not on a diet.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.80,0:25:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她要提早储存能量\N{\rENG}She's storing calories for something.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.21,0:25:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有头绪吗？\N{\rENG}Any ideas?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.22,0:25:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的天\N{\rENG}Oh, my...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.26,0:26:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是…\N{\rENG}Well, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.56,0:26:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看起来像是…\N{\rENG}That looks like some sort of...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.89,0:26:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蛹，像是茧\N{\rENG}chrysalis. Some kind of cocoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.94,0:26:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们在寻找一只巨型飞峨吗？\N{\rENG}What are we looking for, a giant moth?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.78,0:26:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若那是茧...\N{\rENG}If that is a cocoon...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.74,0:26:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她现在一定已完全成长\N{\rENG}She'll be fully-grown now. - Fully-grown.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.45,0:26:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或许她因此而未被我们发现\N{\rENG}Maybe that's how she got by our people.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.16,0:26:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们只在寻找一个孩子\N{\rENG}They were looking for a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.12,0:26:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她的确是孩子\N{\rENG}She is a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.87,0:26:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这儿很臭，我出去了\N{\rENG}It stinks in here. I'm going outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.84,0:26:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向列车长取身分证 和信用卡号码\N{\rENG}Get the conductors' ID and credit card numbers on your computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.84,0:26:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,列车内没有它们影踪\N{\rENG}There's no sign of them on the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.35,0:26:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 她可能带走了他们 - 交给我办\N{\rENG}- Let's assume she took them. - I'll see to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.22,0:26:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她感到受威胁时就会杀人\N{\rENG}She kills if she's threatened.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.73,0:26:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而她是绝无悔意的\N{\rENG}And she has no remorse about it. None.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.73,0:26:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,洛杉矶绝对适合她\N{\rENG}Of course, Los Angeles is perfect for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.36,0:26:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是一个未来的城市\N{\rENG}It's a city of the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.02,0:26:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么事都有可能\N{\rENG}Anything goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.44,0:26:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人口流动性强 大家都是陌生人\N{\rENG}Totally mobile population. Everyone's a stranger.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.70,0:27:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无论她做什么\N{\rENG}Very little is taboo or unacceptable.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.66,0:27:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都不会有人察觉\N{\rENG}Whatever she does, no one will notice her.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.87,0:27:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,随你怎说 所以…\N{\rENG}Well, whatever. So...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.08,0:27:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,洛杉矶将是我们作战的地方\N{\rENG}Los Angeles is where the battle will be fought...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.42,0:27:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要胜利\N{\rENG}...and won.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.48,0:27:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看起来好漂亮\N{\rENG}You look very pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.16,0:27:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一百块的吗？\N{\rENG}Do you have a hundred?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.08,0:27:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这\N{\rENG}Here we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.91,0:27:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小心你的钱 很多人不会像我一样老实\N{\rENG}Be more careful with your money. Not everybody's as honest as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.34,0:27:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你从外地来的？\N{\rENG}Are you foreign?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.09,0:28:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会说英语吗？\N{\rENG}Do you speak English?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.43,0:28:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 会 - 拿着\N{\rENG}- Yes. - Here. You keep this.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.10,0:28:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我替你拿下来\N{\rENG}Here, let me take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.64,0:28:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小心\N{\rENG}Be careful here.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.19,0:28:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会\N{\rENG}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.44,0:28:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小心\N{\rENG}Watch your step.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.54,0:28:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的实验室 〝访客基地一号〞\N{\rENG}Our laboratory, Visitor Base One...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.79,0:28:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...正在迁移到大学现在没用的 病毒研究实验室\N{\rENG}...is being moved to some empty virus research labs at the university.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.46,0:28:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们正在搬运仪器 八点就可以运作\N{\rENG}They're moving our equipment now. It'll be operational by 8:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.22,0:28:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们先进自己房间 十五分钟后会合\N{\rENG}Check into your rooms. Everyone out front in 15 minutes. We'll go over.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.64,0:28:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们将做什么？\N{\rENG}What will we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.31,0:28:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,处理从火车上得来的证据\N{\rENG}Process the evidence from the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.81,0:28:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们能用那生物的DNA 繁殖它吗？\N{\rENG}Could we try growing this creature with its own DNA?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.52,0:29:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次不结合我们的DNA 看看它的脆弱程度\N{\rENG}We do a version without ours this time and investigate its vulnerabilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.98,0:29:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主意不错\N{\rENG}That'd be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.32,0:29:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我也想知道 - 有道理\N{\rENG}- Then I could know how it feels. - Makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.91,0:29:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个人类生命形态可能是掩饰\N{\rENG}This human life form could be a mask. Without the camouflage...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.82,0:29:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错，至少可让我们知道 在对付什么东西\N{\rENG}You're right. At least we'd know what we were dealing with.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.83,0:30:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<font size=28 color=#00d8f8>萨哈拉汽车旅馆
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.59,0:30:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚有两个笨蛋跑掉，我有客人\N{\rENG}A couple of bozos just ran out. I got a customer.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.56,0:30:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 可以帮你吗？ - 我想要个房间\N{\rENG}- Yes, young lady. Can I help you? - I want a room.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.85,0:30:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连税合共六十二元 刚好是蜜月套房的价钱\N{\rENG}62, including tax. That'll just about cover the Honeymoon Suite.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.08,0:30:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好，你经常来吗？\N{\rENG}Hi. Come here often?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.96,0:30:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的星座是什么？\N{\rENG}What's your sign?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.47,0:30:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,厌倦了褐色的头发？\N{\rENG}Tired of brunette?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.93,0:30:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,改变\N{\rENG}Change.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.60,0:31:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,改变你头发的颜色\N{\rENG}Change the color of your hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.15,0:31:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,〝头发色素〞\N{\rENG}Color-Tress.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.66,0:31:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我放大倍数\N{\rENG}I've increased the magnification.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.66,0:31:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当我刺破细胞 外来的DNA就会加进去\N{\rENG}When I pierce the cell, the foreign DNA will be introduced.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.35,0:31:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,岂此有理\N{\rENG}Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.18,0:31:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,摄影机坏了\N{\rENG}The camera's gone down.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.31,0:31:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思\N{\rENG}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.14,0:31:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有另外一部吗？\N{\rENG}Do you have a replacement camera?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.85,0:31:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有，不过替换需要些时间\N{\rENG}We do, but it'll take time for the technician to replace it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.69,0:31:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种事经常在我实验室发生 很简单\N{\rENG}No. This happens in my lab all the time. It's simple to replace it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.53,0:31:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你会替换？\N{\rENG}You saying you can do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.49,0:31:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然，我需要人帮忙\N{\rENG}Sure I can. I just need somebody to give me a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.41,0:31:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,技师不可以进去，是机密\N{\rENG}I don't want technicians in there. This is classified.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.87,0:31:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去\N{\rENG}I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.66,0:32:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去\N{\rENG}I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.04,0:32:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 够爽快，我喜欢 - 我就是这样的\N{\rENG}- Man of action, I like that. - That's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.47,0:32:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请替我扭开那一边，好吗？\N{\rENG}Can you get that one for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.70,0:32:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我摄影机\N{\rENG}Give me the camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.22,0:32:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有些不对劲\N{\rENG}Something's... Something's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.35,0:33:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟，已经开始了\N{\rENG}Christ, It's started already.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.90,0:33:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 把盖子盖上 - 什么？\N{\rENG}- It's started. Get the top back on. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.86,0:33:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把盖子盖上\N{\rENG}Laura, Press, get the top back on.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.24,0:33:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给你\N{\rENG}Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.70,0:33:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她已经把细胞注入了\N{\rENG}She must have penetrated the cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.45,0:33:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 他妈的 - 那是什么？\N{\rENG}- Shit. - What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.74,0:33:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他弄掉了螺钉\N{\rENG}He dropped the bolt.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.75,0:33:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 去找螺钉，盖上盖子 - 我正在试\N{\rENG}- Find the bolt. Get the top on. - I'm looking, Fitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.46,0:33:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们听不到吗？\N{\rENG}Can they hear me in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.13,0:33:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们快点…\N{\rENG}Laura, Press...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.88,0:33:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 盖上盖子，我就让你们出来 - 它去哪了？\N{\rENG}...get the top on, then I'll let you out. - Where'd it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.80,0:33:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 它从铁丝网掉下去了 - 你可提起它吗？\N{\rENG}- It fell through the grate. - Can you lift it up?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.81,0:33:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 移不动它 - 它不动\N{\rENG}- It's not gonna move. - This isn't going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.27,0:33:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 提不起来 - 普雷斯顿…\N{\rENG}- No, can't get it! - Press...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.94,0:33:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...找那螺钉！\N{\rENG}...you gotta get the bolt!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.94,0:33:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我移不动那铁丝网，它被悍接了 - 天啊\N{\rENG}- Can't get it. The floor's welded down. - Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.15,0:33:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天啊\N{\rENG}Press. Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.95,0:33:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我从没见过像这样的东西 - 天啊\N{\rENG}- I've never seen anything like this. - Holy shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.32,0:34:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能让他们出来\N{\rENG}I can't let them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.87,0:34:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 看 - 快点\N{\rENG}- Press, look. - Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.79,0:34:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我们出来！\N{\rENG}Fitch, let us out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.75,0:34:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开门！\N{\rENG}Open the goddamn door!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.58,0:34:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我要知道那里面是什么东西！ - 开门\N{\rENG}- Not until I know what's in there! - Open it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.92,0:34:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 让他们出来 - 不行\N{\rENG}- Let them out. - I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.63,0:34:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 开门 - 让我们出来\N{\rENG}- Open up the fucking door! - Let us out!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.26,0:34:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 告诉我它会停止生长的 - 不会，放他们出来！\N{\rENG}- Tell me it'll stop growing, Dan. - It's not, let them out!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.22,0:34:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开门！\N{\rENG}Open up the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.18,0:34:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,普雷斯顿\N{\rENG}Press, Press.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.14,0:34:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么怪物？!\N{\rENG}What the fuck is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.77,0:34:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去另一扇门\N{\rENG}Laura, get to the other door!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.44,0:34:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 放她出来！ - 不可以！\N{\rENG}- Let her out, Fitch! - I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.65,0:34:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 让她走！ - 不可以\N{\rENG}- Let her out! - I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.65,0:34:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 去你的 - 让她出来\N{\rENG}- You motherfucker! - Let her out!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.49,0:34:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你一定要让他们出来 - 我无法按住它\N{\rENG}- You've gotta let them out! - I can't hold it in!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.20,0:34:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走！\N{\rENG}Get out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.66,0:34:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要烧掉它！\N{\rENG}I'm gonna burn it! Out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.33,0:34:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 这是什么东西？ - 两分钟后这房间就会被烧毁\N{\rENG}- What is this thing? - In 2 minutes, I'm burning the room!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.04,0:34:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我必须这么做\N{\rENG}I have to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.05,0:34:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在两分钟内消灭它\N{\rENG}You have two minutes to kill it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.01,0:34:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,截断煤气管，用它来喷火\N{\rENG}Disconnect the gas line. Use it as a flamethrower.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.10,0:35:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小心\N{\rENG}Laura, watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.52,0:35:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 哪儿？ - 在管子里！\N{\rENG}- Where'd it go? - In the pipes!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.36,0:35:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 开门！ - 住嘴！\N{\rENG}- Open the door! - Shut up, Dan!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.53,0:35:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剩下一分钟\N{\rENG}One minute remaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.54,0:35:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罗拉\N{\rENG}Laura...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.38,0:35:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它不动了，我想我杀了它\N{\rENG}It stopped moving. I think I killed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.96,0:35:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它死了！开门！\N{\rENG}It's dead! Open the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.97,0:35:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让他们出来\N{\rENG}It's dead, Fitch. Let them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.72,0:35:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟，它还没死\N{\rENG}Oh, God, it's not dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.07,0:35:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们怎么办？\N{\rENG}- Shit. - What'll we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.23,0:35:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还剩三十秒\N{\rENG}30 seconds remaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.90,0:36:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 时间不多了，快点 - 开门\N{\rENG}- There's not much time. Let's go. - Open the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.74,0:36:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 快让他们出来 - 不行\N{\rENG}- Let them out. - I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.70,0:36:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我要依循协议书 - 什么协议书？\N{\rENG}- I have to follow protocol! - What protocol?!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.83,0:36:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做这个实验的规则\N{\rENG}The protocols by which we're doing this!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.91,0:36:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你并没告诉他们\N{\rENG}You didn't tell them that before they went in.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.87,0:36:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 让他们出来 - 12 , 11 , 10…\N{\rENG}- Fitch, let them out. - Twelve, 11, 10...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.33,0:36:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 让他们出来！ - 我必须跟从协议书\N{\rENG}- Fitch, let them out! - I must follow protocol.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.09,0:36:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让他们出来\N{\rENG}Let them out, Fitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.67,0:36:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快出来\N{\rENG}Go. Get out of there!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.59,0:36:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,3 , 2 , 1\N{\rENG}Three, two, one.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.26,0:36:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我没有选择  - 是的，当然\N{\rENG}- I had no choice. - Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.22,0:36:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,协议书说若出了状况 就把房间烧毁！\N{\rENG}The protocol is to burn the room if anything went wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.49,0:36:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可在哪儿找到一个男人？\N{\rENG}Where's a good place to find a man?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.83,0:36:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,附近有一家夜总会 那儿有许多男人\N{\rENG}There's plenty of guys at the Id around the corner. It's a club.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.13,0:36:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不会有问题找到男人的\N{\rENG}You won't have trouble meeting somebody there.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.55,0:36:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你\N{\rENG}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.05,0:37:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很容易找到的 有人排队的地方便是了\N{\rENG}You can't miss it. Look for the long line.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.38,0:37:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我需要你的信用卡\N{\rENG}I need your credit card...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.80,0:37:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...以支付你房间杂费 长途电话费等等\N{\rENG}...for room incidentals, long distance calls and so forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.56,0:37:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,信用卡？让我刷刷\N{\rENG}Credit card? Zip zap?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.72,0:37:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美国运通，诸如此类的？\N{\rENG}American Express, Visa, MasterCard?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.48,0:37:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了，谢谢\N{\rENG}There you go. Thanks. All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.31,0:37:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢\N{\rENG}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.15,0:37:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下！\N{\rENG}Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.82,0:37:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不会想让这个落在坏人手里\N{\rENG}You don't want this falling into the wrong hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.03,0:37:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对\N{\rENG}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.29,0:37:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳尔挥杆，被守门员档着\N{\rENG}Here's Justin Crawl. It's through and it's covered by the goalie.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.25,0:37:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂？\N{\rENG}Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.42,0:37:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,列车长的信用卡被发现在…\N{\rENG}The conductor's credit card turned up...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.38,0:37:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...好莱坞旅馆，货车正等着\N{\rENG}...in a Hollywood motel. The van's out front.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.26,0:37:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出发吧\N{\rENG}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.09,0:37:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个\N{\rENG}You two.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.68,0:37:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢享受\N{\rENG}Enjoy yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.60,0:37:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,长腿姐姐，你被看中了 进去\N{\rENG}You, legs. You're in. Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.88,0:38:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你从哪里来的？\N{\rENG}Where are you from?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.05,0:38:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我不是本地人  - 什么？\N{\rENG}- I'm foreign. - You're what?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.47,0:38:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我不是本地人  - 真的？\N{\rENG}- I'm foreign. - Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.39,0:38:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢来\N{\rENG}Easy, easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.72,0:38:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要去派对，但没有男伴\N{\rENG}I've got a party to go to and no one to take me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.77,0:38:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可当你的男伴\N{\rENG}I'll take you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.35,0:38:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你会？ - 是的\N{\rENG}- You will? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.98,0:38:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，我要去洗手间\N{\rENG}Okay. I'm going to the little girls' room.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.31,0:38:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这里等我\N{\rENG}Wait right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.40,0:38:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很快回来\N{\rENG}I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.07,0:38:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会走\N{\rENG}I'll be right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.55,0:39:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不论付出任何代价？\N{\rENG}Whatever it takes, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.63,0:39:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爱情与打仗都是公平的\N{\rENG}All's fair in love and war.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.33,0:39:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看不清楚\N{\rENG}Can't see much on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.83,0:39:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把录影带带回实验室 增强清晰度\N{\rENG}Get this tape to the lab. Enhance it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.91,0:39:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看会否看清楚点\N{\rENG}See if we can get a better look.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.25,0:39:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她样子看起来不错\N{\rENG}She looks nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.17,0:39:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道她去哪里吗？\N{\rENG}Do you have any idea where she went?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.50,0:39:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我去找她  - 她想去找男人\N{\rENG}- I'll find her. - She wanted to meet a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.26,0:39:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我提议她到附近一间夜总会\N{\rENG}I suggested a club called the Id around the corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.97,0:39:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把录影带带回去\N{\rENG}Get the tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.87,0:40:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要去派对，但没有男伴\N{\rENG}I've got a party to go to and no one to take me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.04,0:40:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在哪儿了？\N{\rENG}Where is this party?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.50,0:40:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道\N{\rENG}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.51,0:40:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇,你不能在此停车！\N{\rENG}Whoa, you can't park there!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.14,0:40:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,退回去！\N{\rENG}Back that out!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.22,0:40:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你不可以进去  - 发生什么事？!\N{\rENG}- No, you can't go in there. - What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.91,0:40:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 这儿发生谋杀案  - 不准离开！没有人可以离开！\N{\rENG}- There's been a murder! - No one leaves here! I mean, nobody!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.71,0:41:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这地方总是会有各种行动的\N{\rENG}There's always some action in this part of town.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.55,0:41:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蓝眼睛、金发\N{\rENG}Blue-eyed blonde.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.76,0:41:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,黑色紧身裤、粉红色毛衣 五尺十寸高，她跟谁走的？\N{\rENG}Black leggings, pink sweater, 5' 10" tall. Who'd she leave with?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.94,0:41:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,金发美女跟男人走并非大新闻\N{\rENG}Blonde leaves with a guy is hardly news around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.77,0:41:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说出最受欢迎的人 不要说出没出，急的人\N{\rENG}Name the top attractions. No losers.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.94,0:41:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他会帮她逃走\N{\rENG}Assume he's socially adept. He'll be helping her out.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.44,0:41:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是好人，并非坏蛋\N{\rENG}A friendly guy, not an asshole.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.74,0:41:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在想着\N{\rENG}I'm thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.95,0:41:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 罗比跟一个金发女子离开  - 就是他\N{\rENG}- Robbie left with a blonde. - That's him.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.45,0:41:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是他\N{\rENG}That's him.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.08,0:41:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我带你参观这房子\N{\rENG}Come on. Let me show you the rest of the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.25,0:41:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在那里弄得满身臭汗\N{\rENG}I'm still sweaty from that place.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.79,0:41:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太挤拥了\N{\rENG}It's so crowded.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.59,0:41:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢吗？\N{\rENG}Like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.26,0:41:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢\N{\rENG}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.43,0:41:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想淋浴\N{\rENG}I feel like a shower.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.93,0:42:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想吗？\N{\rENG}You want one?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.31,0:42:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉你\N{\rENG}Tell you what.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.64,0:42:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我现在去淋浴\N{\rENG}I'm taking one.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.31,0:42:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你稍后也想…\N{\rENG}You wanna take one later...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.27,0:42:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有问题\N{\rENG}No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.65,0:42:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,脱去衣服\N{\rENG}Take off your clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.28,0:42:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想看一看\N{\rENG}I want to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.12,0:43:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好美\N{\rENG}Very nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.22,0:43:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,送我回去好吗？\N{\rENG}Take me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.76,0:43:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么？\N{\rENG}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.97,0:43:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道为何我们要来这\N{\rENG}You know why we came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.47,0:43:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我改变主意了\N{\rENG}I've changed my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.85,0:43:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说〝不〞\N{\rENG}All right. You said "no."
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.81,0:43:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我听到了，过来\N{\rENG}It's duly noted. Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.39,0:43:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想离开！\N{\rENG}I wanna go!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.56,0:43:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太迟了，你休想离开！\N{\rENG}Too late. You're not leaving! You're not!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.57,0:43:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 好吧  - 这才像样\N{\rENG}- All right. - That's better.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.29,0:45:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么回事？在夜总会杀掉女子 又杀掉这家伙\N{\rENG}What's happening? Kills a girl at the club, kills this guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.04,0:45:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她像是精神病患者\N{\rENG}I'd say she fits the definition of a psychopath.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.29,0:45:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没什么会抑制她\N{\rENG}Nothing inhibits her.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.54,0:45:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没道德观念，没社会结构\N{\rENG}No moral sense, no social structure.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.80,0:45:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她并非沉溺在母爱之中\N{\rENG}She wasn't exactly smothered with a mother's love or taught good manners.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.64,0:45:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,究竟发生了什么事\N{\rENG}I asked what was happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.89,0:45:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他做了一些事使她生气\N{\rENG}He did something, she was angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.97,0:45:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若她感到受威胁或有人阻碍她 她就会杀死对方\N{\rENG}She'll kill if she's threatened or if anyone gets in her way.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.14,0:45:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阻碍她什么？\N{\rENG}Of what?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.56,0:45:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她的生命周期\N{\rENG}Her life cycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.06,0:45:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她似乎想交配\N{\rENG}I think she's trying to mate.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.61,0:45:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进行繁殖\N{\rENG}Reproduce.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.77,0:45:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\rENG}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.32,0:45:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为何她要杀那女子？\N{\rENG}So why did she kill the girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.32,0:45:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,性竞争\N{\rENG}Sexual competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.32,0:45:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她不会在竞争上屈服\N{\rENG}She's hard on the competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.20,0:45:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她想交配\N{\rENG}Now she managed to mate.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.08,0:45:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,似乎不成功，他仍穿着裤子\N{\rENG}Doesn't look like a success. He's still got his pants on.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.00,0:45:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 她很沮丧  - 谁不会？\N{\rENG}- She's frustrated. - Who isn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.50,0:45:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她有什么问题？是她跟他来的\N{\rENG}What's her problem? She was here with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.33,0:45:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或许她拒绝他\N{\rENG}Maybe she rejected him.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.17,0:46:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她大概有特别感官\N{\rENG}She probably has special senses.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.26,0:46:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老鼠能够感应配偶 是否有病或基因不健全的\N{\rENG}Rats can sense diseased or genetic damage in their potential mates...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.76,0:46:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...所以我们可以测试他\N{\rENG}...so we can test his body...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.43,0:46:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...检查他有没有遗传病或缺憾 让他不能做她的...\N{\rENG}...for hereditary diseases or defects that would make him a loser...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.18,0:46:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...配偶\N{\rENG}...essentially.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.77,0:46:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是注射针\N{\rENG}Needles.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.69,0:46:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许他是瘾君子 或是糖尿病人\N{\rENG}Maybe he was a doper, or a diabetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.02,0:46:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,两者都不能够接受 对不起\N{\rENG}Either way would make him unacceptable. Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.94,0:46:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是了\N{\rENG}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.45,0:46:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胰岛素，他是糖尿病患者\N{\rENG}Insulin. Diabetic. There you have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.87,0:46:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她可以离开的 为何要杀死他？\N{\rENG}She could have just walked out. Why kill him?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.79,0:46:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他让她生气\N{\rENG}He pissed her off.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.12,0:46:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有些家伙被拒绝了 也死缠烂打的\N{\rENG}Some men, when rejected, get insistent.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.79,0:46:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 追踪他的汽车  - 已发了通报\N{\rENG}- Put an APB out on his car. - We have.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.63,0:46:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要返回旅馆 我要查个水落石出\N{\rENG}We'll go back to the motel. I want to check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.96,0:46:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还说比较温驯和易受控制？\N{\rENG}More docile and controllable, huh, Fitch?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.44,0:47:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你认为怎样？ - 我认为怎样？\N{\rENG}- What do you think, Dan? - What do I think?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.82,0:47:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想她现在想独自一人\N{\rENG}I think she'd want to be alone now.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.20,0:47:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么多辆车停在外面 她是不会来的\N{\rENG}She won't come here with all these cars outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.74,0:47:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你指她自有方法回来？\N{\rENG}You're assuming she could find her way back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.91,0:47:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有可能\N{\rENG}She could.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.75,0:47:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么？\N{\rENG}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.58,0:47:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许是经血\N{\rENG}Maybe menstrual blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.42,0:47:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果她有经期 即是她可以繁殖\N{\rENG}If she's menstruating, she can reproduce.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.26,0:47:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对，我知道\N{\rENG}Yes, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.35,0:49:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕\N{\rENG}Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.19,0:49:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天\N{\rENG}Oh, Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.90,0:49:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请让开\N{\rENG}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.07,0:49:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快叫救护车来 谁人有电话？\N{\rENG}Call a paramedic! Anybody got a phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.41,0:49:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十号公路向西行的交通\N{\rENG}If your commute takes you westbound on the 10 freeway...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.50,0:49:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...将有一小时的延误\N{\rENG}...expect an hour delay.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.25,0:49:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,往．马里布的车程将会缓慢\N{\rENG}The drive will be slow to Malibu.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.84,0:49:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<font size=28 color=#00d8f8>只限无铅汽油
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.60,0:49:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,录影带的清晰度仍不理想\N{\rENG}The video enhancement is not that great.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.35,0:49:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你猜她多大？ 二十岁？二十三岁？\N{\rENG}How old do you think she is? Twenty, 23?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.35,0:49:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她的生殖系统应该完全成熟\N{\rENG}Her reproductive system should be fully developed.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.19,0:49:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她的生理时钟必定很亢奋\N{\rENG}Her biological clock must be in hyperdrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.40,0:49:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她想要孩子\N{\rENG}She wants a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.57,0:49:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若她有孩子，我们就有麻烦\N{\rENG}If she has a child our problems have just begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.53,0:49:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若她怀着的是个男孩 而他的成长速度如西尔一样\N{\rENG}If her offspring is male and develops at the same rate as Sil...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.87,0:50:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...六个月后就有能力繁殖了\N{\rENG}...it could reproduce in 6 months.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.79,0:50:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天晓得他能使多少个女性怀孕\N{\rENG}God knows how many females it could impregnate.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.46,0:50:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,菲奇\N{\rENG}Fitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.46,0:50:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当一个掠食性品种来到\N{\rENG}When a predatory species is introduced...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.75,0:50:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...一个封闭的生态系统\N{\rENG}...into a closed ecological system...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.59,0:50:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...较弱的品种就会灭绝\N{\rENG}...the extinction of the weaker species is inevitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.84,0:50:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们在圣莫尼卡 找到已没汽油的宝．马\N{\rENG}They found the murdered guy's BMW, out of gas in Santa Monica.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.93,0:50:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她叫什么名字？\N{\rENG}What's her name?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.26,0:50:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我不知道  - 你是谁？\N{\rENG}- I don't know. - Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.64,0:50:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她没有身分证 我想确定她没大碍\N{\rENG}She didn't have any ID. I thought I'd make sure she was okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.94,0:50:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她有医疗保险吗？\N{\rENG}You think she's got insurance?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.94,0:50:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道 算在我信用卡的帐上吧\N{\rENG}I don't know. Just put it on my credit card for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.98,0:50:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你连她的名字也不知道 像你这样的人真难得\N{\rENG}And you don't know her name. Guys like you are hard to find.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.95,0:50:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让实验室做个实验\N{\rENG}Get a lab workup on that, stat.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.33,0:50:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给她照X光片，要照这里\N{\rENG}Get her up to x-ray. I want an x-ray on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.29,0:50:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看似是肩胛骨碎裂\N{\rENG}It looks like a scapula fracture.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.14,0:51:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的肩膀\N{\rENG}Your shoulder wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.14,0:51:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎会这样的？\N{\rENG}What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.36,0:51:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,医生，我们现在需要你.一个孩子烧伤刚进来\N{\rENG}Doctor, we need you now. A child burn victim just came in.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.11,0:51:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 这是怎么回事？ - 请医生\N{\rENG}- What is going on here? - Doctor, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.16,0:51:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天！你看到她的肩膀吗？\N{\rENG}Jesus Christ! Did you see her shoulder?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.95,0:51:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请你立刻过去\N{\rENG}Please. We need you immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.88,0:51:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没事\N{\rENG}You're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.51,0:51:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没事\N{\rENG}I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.84,0:51:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你受了重伤的\N{\rENG}I was sure you were seriously injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.88,0:51:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没事\N{\rENG}I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.34,0:51:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这真是奇迹\N{\rENG}You are. It's a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.22,0:51:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以离开了吗？\N{\rENG}Can we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.56,0:51:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,医生说你可以离开吗？\N{\rENG}Did the doctor say you could go?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.52,0:51:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是\N{\rENG}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.10,0:51:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们会派人到那边\N{\rENG}We'll send somebody over there. Thanks a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.36,0:52:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕克湾医院的医生 说有怪事发生\N{\rENG}Doctor over at Parkbay Hospital called in with some weird story.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.03,0:52:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,查查看，只在数英里外\N{\rENG}We should check it out. It's a few miles away.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.53,0:52:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罗拉\N{\rENG}Laura...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.20,0:52:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...普雷斯顿，查探一下\N{\rENG}...Press, take a car, check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.54,0:52:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 帕克湾医院？ - 对，帕克湾\N{\rENG}- Parkbay Hospital?  - Yeah, Parkbay.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.50,0:52:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她用走的\N{\rENG}She walked.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.88,0:52:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她用走的\N{\rENG}She walked.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.55,0:52:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她沿着那边走…\N{\rENG}She walked that way...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.38,0:52:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...就在不久之前\N{\rENG}...not too long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.02,0:52:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃些水果和起司吧\N{\rENG}Got some fruit and cheese.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.06,0:52:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么？\N{\rENG}What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.69,0:52:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你指那热水池？\N{\rENG}You mean the hot tub?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.19,0:52:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,热水池\N{\rENG}A hot tub.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.90,0:52:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我爱这个地方\N{\rENG}I love this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.45,0:52:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,远离车辆、人和事\N{\rENG}It's away from the traffic and business and people.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.70,0:52:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有时觉得自己并不在洛杉矶\N{\rENG}Sometimes it feels like you're not in L.A. Anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.87,0:52:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过来\N{\rENG}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.37,0:52:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要永远留住这一刻\N{\rENG}We'll immortalize the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.30,0:53:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看着摄影机\N{\rENG}Look at the camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.10,0:53:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 她的骨骼重生了 - 是她\N{\rENG}- This girl literally reformed her bones. - It's her.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.56,0:53:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁帮她挂号的？\N{\rENG}Who checked her in?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.15,0:53:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然我们看看\N{\rENG}I don't know. Let's find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.23,0:53:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她没有保险 所以他用信用卡帮她付了帐\N{\rENG}She had no insurance so this guy put it on his own credit card.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.57,0:53:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是这个档案，他叫约翰凯瑞\N{\rENG}Here's the file. John F. Carey.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.07,0:53:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有驾．驶执照或地址的资料吗？\N{\rENG}You don't have a driver's license or home address?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.95,0:53:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有 只有他的信用卡刷卡纪录\N{\rENG}No, sir. Just an imprint of his credit card.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.42,0:53:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我们印一张你有的资料\N{\rENG}Give us a printout of what you've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.75,0:53:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没问题\N{\rENG}No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.30,0:53:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃糖吗？\N{\rENG}Some candy?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.52,0:53:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在帕利塞德 还有他的电话号码\N{\rENG}It's in the Palisades and he's got a phone number.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.48,0:53:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉菲奇我们的目的地 试着打电话给约翰凯瑞\N{\rENG}Tell Fitch where we're headed, and try to get John Carey on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.55,0:54:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我去接\N{\rENG}I'd better get the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.69,0:54:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,答录机响了，应该留话吗？\N{\rENG}I've got his machine. Should I leave a message?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.23,0:54:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\rENG}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.73,0:54:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉他他将要跟 外太空生物交配\N{\rENG}Tell him he's about to copulate with a creature from outer space.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.20,0:54:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 交配？ - 对\N{\rENG}- Copulate, huh? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.70,0:54:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你\N{\rENG}I like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.20,0:54:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道\N{\rENG}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.37,0:55:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们在一起也不会太快\N{\rENG}It's not too soon for us to be together.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.13,0:55:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对，不会太快\N{\rENG}No, it's not too soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.96,0:55:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不用穿裤子\N{\rENG}You don't need these.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.72,0:55:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你太急了\N{\rENG}Hey, hey. That's a little fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.32,0:55:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？\N{\rENG}What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.23,0:55:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢来\N{\rENG}Take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.40,0:55:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放松点\N{\rENG}Just relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.57,0:55:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有许多时间\N{\rENG}There's plenty of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.67,0:55:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？\N{\rENG}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.59,0:55:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人在门外\N{\rENG}I think someone's at the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.80,0:55:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别走\N{\rENG}Don't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.76,0:55:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求求你 我想要孩子\N{\rENG}Please. I want a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.18,0:55:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？! 对不起？\N{\rENG}What?! Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.61,0:56:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从旁边去看看\N{\rENG}Let's go around the side.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.78,0:56:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外面\N{\rENG}Outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.48,0:58:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 什么事？ - 是松鼠！该死的松鼠！\N{\rENG}- What happened?  - A squirrel! A fucking squirrel!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.82,0:58:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 她曾在这儿 - 没错\N{\rENG}- She was here. - Yeah, she was.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.49,0:58:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想确定她离开了\N{\rENG}I wanna make sure she's not still here.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.81,0:59:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应检查尸体 有没有曾性交过的迹象\N{\rENG}Perhaps we should check the body for evidence that they've had sex.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.48,0:59:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,血淋淋的情景叫我害怕\N{\rENG}I used to be scared at the sight of blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.65,0:59:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已习惯了\N{\rENG}Now I guess I'm getting used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.74,0:59:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对啊\N{\rENG}Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.02,1:00:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 救我！ - 什么事？\N{\rENG}- Help me, please! - Oh, my God. What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.81,1:00:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们在客厅发现的\N{\rENG}We found this in the living room.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.53,1:00:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她喜欢他\N{\rENG}She liked him.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.69,1:00:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不够清楚\N{\rENG}Well, not enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.03,1:00:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟录像监测所拍出来的差不多\N{\rENG}Can't see any more on that than we did on the video monitor.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.66,1:00:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他没有帮她拍到一张好相片\N{\rENG}He didn't get a good picture of her.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.79,1:00:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水里没发现精液\N{\rENG}There's no evidence of semen in the hot tub water.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.33,1:00:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许她带走了\N{\rENG}Maybe she took it with.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.04,1:00:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么她没有交配\N{\rENG}So she probably hasn't managed to mate.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.46,1:00:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我们打扰了她  - 是的，应该是\N{\rENG}- We interrupted her. - Yes, I think we did.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.71,1:00:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我些我可以用的\N{\rENG}Give me something I can use.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.18,1:00:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你最近想到了什么？\N{\rENG}What have you come up with lately, Fitch?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.72,1:00:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她不怕我们\N{\rENG}She's not scared of us.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.64,1:00:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是肯定的\N{\rENG}That's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.77,1:00:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们被难倒了\N{\rENG}We're all beat.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.61,1:01:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先回旅馆休，急一下\N{\rENG}We'll go back to the hotel and rest.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:01.40,1:01:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明晚\N{\rENG}Tomorrow night...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.32,1:01:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...我们再回到夜总会\N{\rENG}...we'll go back to the club.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.24,1:01:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 进行监视  - 进行监视\N{\rENG}- Stake it out. - Stake it out.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.00,1:01:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她并不蠢\N{\rENG}She's not stupid.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.41,1:01:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她不会重蹈覆辙\N{\rENG}She won't repeat herself.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.17,1:01:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没理由再去那里 那儿提供了个坏榜样\N{\rENG}There's no point going there. It provided a poor specimen.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:17.63,1:01:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很难说\N{\rENG}I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.84,1:01:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她只来了两天，只知道那地方\N{\rENG}She's been in the city two days. It's what she knows.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:21.76,1:01:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我宁愿再到夜总会看看\N{\rENG}I'd rather try the club...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.68,1:01:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,..不要只坐在指挥中心 回忆着我们多接近成功\N{\rENG}...than sit at the command center reminiscing about how close we got.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.48,1:01:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她可会是厉害的生物武器\N{\rENG}She would make one excellent biological weapon.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.49,1:01:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若有人认为我们是 散布宇宙间的…\N{\rENG}If someone thought we were some kind of galactic weed that would...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.66,1:01:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...银河系废物\N{\rENG}...spread through the universe.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.79,1:01:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的意思是...\N{\rENG}So what you're saying is that...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.33,1:01:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...她是疗药，而我们是病源\N{\rENG}...she's the cure and we're the disease.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.13,1:01:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说得好\N{\rENG}That's well said.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.71,1:02:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,〝罗拉贝克〞\N{\rENG}"Baker, Laura.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.46,1:02:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,〝加州锡米谷 米德大道1735号〞\N{\rENG}1735 Meander Drive, Simi v alley, california."
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.38,1:02:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你吗？\N{\rENG}That's you, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.55,1:02:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我上次查的资料是这样的\N{\rENG}Last time I checked.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.72,1:02:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在这做什么？\N{\rENG}What do you do for kicks out there?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.89,1:02:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怀念像你这样的家伙\N{\rENG}Pine for guys like you.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.14,1:02:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我正这样想\N{\rENG}That's what I thought.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.21,1:02:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们饿吗？\N{\rENG}So anyone hungry?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.42,1:02:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，我很疲倦，我想去休息\N{\rENG}No, thanks. I'm beat. I'm gonna try to get some sleep.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.22,1:02:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 晚安  - 晚安\N{\rENG}- Good night. - Yeah. Night.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.72,1:02:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我可以跟你一起吃  - 谢了\N{\rENG}- I'll have something to eat with you. - Thanks, Dan.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.45,1:03:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你做过噩梦吗？ - 做过\N{\rENG}- Do you ever have nightmares? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.79,1:03:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请松绑我的双手\N{\rENG}Please untie my hands.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:00.29,1:04:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我不会伤害你的  - 我做了噩梦\N{\rENG}- I wouldn't hurt you. Please. - I have them.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.59,1:04:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噩梦想告诉我我是谁\N{\rENG}I think they tell me who I am.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.92,1:04:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你为何要这样做？\N{\rENG}Why are you doing this to me?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.47,1:04:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道为何我在这里\N{\rENG}I don't know why I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.47,1:04:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道我是谁，谁派我来\N{\rENG}I don't know who I am, who sent me.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.77,1:04:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你知道吗？ - 不！\N{\rENG}- Do you? - No!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.27,1:04:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你为何在此？ - 我不知道\N{\rENG}- Why do you think you're here? - I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.28,1:04:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请放过我\N{\rENG}Please let me go.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.11,1:04:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求求你，让我走\N{\rENG}Please. Please, let me go.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.87,1:04:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会伤害你\N{\rENG}I wouldn't hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.12,1:04:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我保证\N{\rENG}I promise.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.87,1:04:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我不会伤害你的  - 你会的\N{\rENG}- I wouldn't hurt you. - Yes, you would.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.96,1:04:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是你还不知道\N{\rENG}You just don't know it yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.38,1:04:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会！\N{\rENG}No, I wouldn't!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:47.80,1:04:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求求你！\N{\rENG}Please!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:50.80,1:04:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我双手很疼\N{\rENG}My hands are hurting me.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:57.47,1:04:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你\N{\rENG}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.60,1:05:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你\N{\rENG}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.57,1:05:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的天！\N{\rENG}Oh, my God!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.42,1:05:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不！\N{\rENG}Oh, my God, no!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.17,1:05:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天，不！\N{\rENG}No! No!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.41,1:06:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<font size=28 color=#00d8f8>危险，高电压
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.71,1:07:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罗拉和普雷斯顿喜欢对方\N{\rENG}Laura and Press, they like each other.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.13,1:07:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们不流露自己的感受\N{\rENG}They just don't like to show how they feel.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.17,1:07:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？\N{\rENG}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.42,1:07:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罗拉和普雷斯顿 喜欢对方\N{\rENG}Laura and Press, they like each other.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.34,1:07:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,随你怎说吧，丹\N{\rENG}Yeah, whatever you say, Dan.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.30,1:07:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这儿烟雾弥漫，我打算出去\N{\rENG}Look, it's really smoky in here. I'm gonna go outside, get some air.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.85,1:07:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在货车上歇一歇 这简直是浪费时间\N{\rENG}Think I'll lie down in the van. Have a rest. This is a complete waste of time.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.85,1:07:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉上像是在浪费时间吗？\N{\rENG}Get a feeling you're on a wild goose chase?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.90,1:07:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对\N{\rENG}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.48,1:07:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请让开\N{\rENG}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.38,1:09:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滚出去，这是我的地盘\N{\rENG}Get out of here. This is my trashcan.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:12.48,1:09:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你\N{\rENG}It's you.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.94,1:09:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂\N{\rENG}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.95,1:09:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她在这儿\N{\rENG}She's here! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.37,1:09:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-是她吗？ -是\N{\rENG}- Dan. Is that her? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.41,1:09:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这儿\N{\rENG}Here.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.09,1:09:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上车\N{\rENG}Get in the van.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:44.63,1:09:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上车！\N{\rENG}Everybody get in the van!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.10,1:09:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们朝山区走 我们需要直升机\N{\rENG}They're heading into the hills. We'll need the helicopters.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.66,1:10:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要上尼科斯峡谷 在茂贺兰拦截她\N{\rENG}We're going up Nichols canyon. One of you try to block her at Mulholland.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.22,1:10:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小心\N{\rENG}Watch it!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.20,1:11:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的天！\N{\rENG}Oh, my God!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.03,1:12:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已封锁道路 我们一定得告诉报界些消息\N{\rENG}We blocked the road. We've gotta tell the press something.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:14.99,1:12:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,随便你怎么告诉他们 但别说出事实\N{\rENG}Tell them what you want, just don't tell them the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:18.08,1:12:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不认为她会在夜总会出现 那太简单了\N{\rENG}I don't buy her showing up at the club. It's too damn convenient.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.87,1:12:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,眼见为实 你不相信你双眼吗？\N{\rENG}Seeing is believing or don't you trust your eyes?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:24.59,1:12:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回去！叫这些人统统回去！\N{\rENG}Get back! Get all these people back!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.00,1:12:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有些不对\N{\rENG}Fitch. Fitch. It doesn't feel right.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.34,1:12:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,长官！\N{\rENG}Sir!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:31.76,1:12:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们在其中一道车门 发现一只断指\N{\rENG}We found a severed thumb in one of the doors that got ripped off.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:35.68,1:12:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 让我看看  - 她或许给夹在门中\N{\rENG}- Let me see that. - She may have caught it in the door.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.10,1:12:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿去实验室，看看是否属于她\N{\rENG}Get to the lab, see if it's hers.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.52,1:12:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 可从基因上辨别出来  - 这件事完了\N{\rENG}- It'll be genetically identifiable. - It's all over, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:44.73,1:12:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天你可重过自己的生活\N{\rENG}Tomorrow you can go back to your lives.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.28,1:12:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你们，做得好\N{\rENG}Congratulations on a job well done.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.11,1:12:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就这样结束了？\N{\rENG}Just like that, huh, Fitch?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:55.78,1:12:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不认为\N{\rENG}I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:08.00,1:13:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,留话给我 法兰克，我会和你吃晚餮\N{\rENG}Leave me a message. And Frank, I'm going to dinner.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.80,1:13:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们在哪见面？再见\N{\rENG}Where are we meeting? Bye, sweetie.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.14,1:13:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,服务生\N{\rENG}Waiter.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:19.85,1:13:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我猜我们赢了\N{\rENG}Well, I guess we won.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:22.64,1:13:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我们赢了，科学输了  - 我不认为我们会这样赢\N{\rENG}- We won, science lost. - I didn't think we'd get her this way.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:27.65,1:13:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 没那么容易  - 你会怀念她吗？\N{\rENG}- Not that easy. - You sound like you'll miss her.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:29.94,1:13:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会的\N{\rENG}I guess I will.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.03,1:13:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想我尊重她\N{\rENG}I think I respected her.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.16,1:13:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这的确是不好做的工作 但我很高兴跟你们三人合作\N{\rENG}I know this was a hellish job, but I really enjoyed working with you three.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:40.70,1:13:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然国税局请客 让我们再多喝一杯\N{\rENG}And since Uncle Sam is buying, let's have another round.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.96,1:13:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,服务生！\N{\rENG}Waiter!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:45.12,1:13:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不喝酒的\N{\rENG}I don't... I don't drink.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:47.34,1:13:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚你会的\N{\rENG}Don't worry, Dan. Tonight you will.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:51.01,1:13:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想跳舞吗？\N{\rENG}You wanna dance?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:52.67,1:13:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 谁？我？ - 没错\N{\rENG}- Who, me? - Yeah, you.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:57.97,1:14:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 好  - 对啊\N{\rENG}- All right. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:16.16,1:14:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你没家室 在纽约有女朋友吗？\N{\rENG}I know you don't have a family. Do you have a girlfriend in New York?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:21.87,1:14:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,曾经有几个，不过都不久\N{\rENG}I guess I've had a few, but they don't hang around very long.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:26.17,1:14:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能我有太多秘密\N{\rENG}I guess I keep too many secrets.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:28.96,1:14:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我分享一个\N{\rENG}You wanna share one with me?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:31.34,1:14:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 现在？ - 对\N{\rENG}- Right now? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.22,1:14:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你是做什么的 吓不到我的\N{\rENG}I know what you do, and it doesn't scare me.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:41.85,1:14:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 真的？ - 真的\N{\rENG}- Really? - No.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:44.52,1:14:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但却使许多人害怕\N{\rENG}Well, it does most people.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:50.94,1:14:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还要再见你\N{\rENG}I wouldn't wanna never see you again.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:00.66,1:15:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 喂  - 你在...?\N{\rENG}- Hey. - What are you...?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:02.08,1:15:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我认错人\N{\rENG}I'm sorry. I'm sorry. I thought you were somebody else.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:06.16,1:15:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起\N{\rENG}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:09.50,1:15:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事吗？\N{\rENG}You okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:10.92,1:15:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以为是西尔 我见到一头金发\N{\rENG}I thought it was Sil. I saw the blonde hair.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:13.75,1:15:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她死了\N{\rENG}She's dead, Press.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:15.42,1:15:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拇指的化验，证明是她的\N{\rENG}The tests on the thumb proved it was her.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.18,1:15:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你相信化验，而我则有胆识 我不相信\N{\rENG}You got your test and I got my gut. I just don't buy it.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:22.10,1:15:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要你还感到她存在 你都不会放弃\N{\rENG}I think as long as you feel she's out there, you got a mission.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:26.27,1:15:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或者你不想结束这任务\N{\rENG}Maybe you don't want this job to be over.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:29.52,1:15:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或者是，那又如何？\N{\rENG}Well, maybe not. So what?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:35.11,1:15:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你那支舞\N{\rENG}Thanks for the dance.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:51.25,1:15:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安\N{\rENG}Good night.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:59.51,1:16:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么？\N{\rENG}What do you call this?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:01.14,1:16:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,长岛冰茶\N{\rENG}It's called a Long Island Ice Tea.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:04.60,1:16:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有茶的成分吗？\N{\rENG}It's got tea in it?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:06.93,1:16:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有\N{\rENG}Nope.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:25.62,1:16:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很香，我可以试试吗？\N{\rENG}Smells nice, can I try some?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.45,1:16:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请便\N{\rENG}Help yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:35.17,1:16:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这会迷倒你男朋友吗？\N{\rENG}Does it work on your boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:37.17,1:16:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,令他厌恶\N{\rENG}Yeah. As a repellent.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.01,1:16:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他这个年纪 身型还保持得很好\N{\rENG}I don't know. I think he's in remarkably good shape for a man his age.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:58.15,1:17:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一杯长岛冰茶\N{\rENG}One Long Island Ice Tea.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:02.49,1:17:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢这些茶\N{\rENG}I like these cups of tea.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:07.03,1:17:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 什么？ - 太好了\N{\rENG}- What? - That's great.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:15.04,1:17:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿，给我一杯\N{\rENG}Hey, give me one of those.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:17.75,1:17:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢这些茶\N{\rENG}I like these cups of tea, man.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:21.26,1:17:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很累，我要去睡了\N{\rENG}You guys, I'm tired. I'm gonna go to bed.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:26.89,1:17:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎样？\N{\rENG}So?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:29.77,1:17:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她说要上床睡觉\N{\rENG}She's going to bed.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:31.27,1:17:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错\N{\rENG}I guess.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:34.60,1:17:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但她仍然...\N{\rENG}She still...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.23,1:17:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...想见你\N{\rENG}...wants to see you though.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:42.74,1:17:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去看看你的话是否正确\N{\rENG}Maybe I'll go find out if you're right about that.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:11.35,1:18:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地震时我不想在这里\N{\rENG}I'd hate to be in here during an earthquake.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:13.68,1:18:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错\N{\rENG}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:15.44,1:18:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到哪一层？\N{\rENG}What floor do you want?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:17.44,1:18:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十楼，麻烦你\N{\rENG}Ten, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:28.95,1:18:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你的香水\N{\rENG}I like your perfume.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:31.62,1:18:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？\N{\rENG}You do?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:33.45,1:18:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 谢谢  - 对不起，我要出去\N{\rENG}- Thank you. - Excuse me. I get out here.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:40.88,1:18:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安\N{\rENG}Good night.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.08,1:19:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你好 - 你好\N{\rENG}- Hi. - Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.51,1:19:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<font size=28 color=#00d8f8>请勿打扰
Dialogue: 0,1:19:38.77,1:19:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想要什么吗？\N{\rENG}Did you want something?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:41.27,1:19:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 也许 - 也许？\N{\rENG}- Maybe. - Maybe?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:29.36,1:20:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打扫房间\N{\rENG}Housekeeping.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:32.41,1:20:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丹\N{\rENG}Dan. Dan.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:35.53,1:20:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我猜那两个女子 会喜欢像我们这样不平凡的男人\N{\rENG}Those two over there. Bet they like unusual men like us.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.04,1:20:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女人觉得我很奇怪\N{\rENG}Women think I'm strange.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:42.42,1:20:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有点不舒服\N{\rENG}I don't feel well.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:44.29,1:20:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别说傻话\N{\rENG}Don't be silly.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:46.38,1:20:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过去跟她们聊天\N{\rENG}Just go over there and talk to them.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:48.71,1:20:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要走了 我觉得你该跟我一起走，好吗？\N{\rENG}I have to go. And I think you should leave with me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:54.43,1:20:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想多留一会\N{\rENG}I'm gonna stay for a while, actually.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:59.43,1:21:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\rENG}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:01.73,1:21:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天见\N{\rENG}I'll see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:06.15,1:21:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打扫房间\N{\rENG}House keeping.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:22.54,1:21:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你好 - 你好\N{\rENG}- Hi. - Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:24.00,1:21:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在那边坐着，我在猜…\N{\rENG}I was sitting over there, wondering...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:26.63,1:21:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...这两位聪明漂亮的女子 怎么没有男伴\N{\rENG}...what two intelligent, glamorous women were doing without dates.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:30.38,1:21:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫史蒂文阿登\N{\rENG}My name's Stephen Arden.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:32.13,1:21:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在哈佛教授人类学的\N{\rENG}I teach anthropology at Harvard.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:34.47,1:21:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我曾住在波士顿  - 是吗？\N{\rENG}- I lived in Boston once. - Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:36.30,1:21:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一年\N{\rENG}For a year.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:37.68,1:21:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 冷得要命  - 的确很冷\N{\rENG}- Froze my butt off. - It's cold in Boston.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:40.81,1:21:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们是比尔和东尼 我忘了你的名字\N{\rENG}This is Bill and Tony. I forget your name.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:48.94,1:21:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有趣的袜子\N{\rENG}Cute little socks.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:52.15,1:21:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,起来\N{\rENG}Stand up.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.57,1:22:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么能进来的？\N{\rENG}How'd you get in here?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:35.49,1:22:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 偷了钥匙  - 什么？\N{\rENG}- I stole the key. - What?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.20,1:22:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在楼下见到你\N{\rENG}I saw you downstairs, but you were with all those people.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:41.83,1:22:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我就上来等你\N{\rENG}So I thought I'd come up and wait.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:47.17,1:22:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种事不经常发生在我身上\N{\rENG}This kind of thing doesn't usually happen to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:51.34,1:22:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想跟你一起\N{\rENG}I just want to be with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:03.47,1:23:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了\N{\rENG}Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:19.36,1:23:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用做安全措施吗？\N{\rENG}What about protection?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:16.17,1:24:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她在这儿\N{\rENG}She's here. She's here.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:47.20,1:24:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,普雷斯顿\N{\rENG}Press?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:49.00,1:24:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人在门外\N{\rENG}Someone's at the door.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:52.75,1:24:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是谁？\N{\rENG}Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:53.92,1:24:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,普雷斯顿，罗拉\N{\rENG}Press, Laura.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:55.29,1:24:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是丹，我有事告诉你\N{\rENG}It's Dan. I gotta talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:57.71,1:25:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他到底想怎样？\N{\rENG}Christ, what does he want?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:10.10,1:25:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 什么事？ - 我有不祥预感\N{\rENG}- What's the problem, Dan? - I just got this terrible feeling.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:13.19,1:25:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我奇怪地想到 西尔跟阿登一起的影像\N{\rENG}I get this strange thought, this image of Sil with Arden.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:16.52,1:25:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,西尔跟阿登\N{\rENG}Sil's next door with Arden, Press.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:18.36,1:25:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可能，她已死了\N{\rENG}No, no, no. She's dead, Dan.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:21.03,1:25:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我经过他房间 听到里面有另外一人\N{\rENG}I went to his room and there's someone in there with him.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.87,1:25:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你有敲门吗？ - 有，但我不知道她会做什么\N{\rENG}- Did you knock on the door? - Yes, but I don't know what she'll do.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:28.66,1:25:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们很吵，他们在做爱\N{\rENG}They're making a lot of noise. They're having sex.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:32.66,1:25:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道是西尔\N{\rENG}I know it's Sil, I know it!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:35.54,1:25:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\rENG}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:36.84,1:25:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你，我去穿衣\N{\rENG}I believe you. I'll get dressed.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:54.94,1:25:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你使我欲仙欲死\N{\rENG}I enjoyed that immensely.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:15.29,1:26:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我感觉到了 - 什么？\N{\rENG}- I felt it. - What?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:21.46,1:26:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开始了\N{\rENG}It's started.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:23.76,1:26:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？\N{\rENG}What's started?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:25.55,1:26:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生命\N{\rENG}Life.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:27.89,1:26:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真可爱\N{\rENG}Oh, my darling girl.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:30.47,1:26:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在某些文化里，女人相信 她们知道自己何时怀孕\N{\rENG}In some cultures, women believe they know the moment of conception...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:34.85,1:26:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不相信我？感觉一下\N{\rENG}Don't you believe me? Feel.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:42.03,1:26:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天啊！\N{\rENG}Holy shit!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:49.53,1:26:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望你说得对\N{\rENG}I hope you're right about this, Dan.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:03.88,1:27:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 她朝地下室去了  - 我们走楼梯\N{\rENG}- She's headed for the basement. - We'll take the stairs.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:06.47,1:27:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罗拉，跟我来！\N{\rENG}Laura, come with me!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:08.09,1:27:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来！\N{\rENG}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:12.26,1:27:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果她怀孕了 我们必须在她生产前找到她\N{\rENG}If she's pregnant, we gotta get to her before she gives birth.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:16.60,1:27:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们不知道我们在跟什么周旋\N{\rENG}God. We don't know what we're dealing with here.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:19.69,1:27:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她可以生一打孩子 甚至可产一千个卵\N{\rENG}She could have a dozen babies. She could lay 1000 eggs!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:23.73,1:27:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有见到阿登吗？\N{\rENG}Oh, God. Did you see Arden?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:27.28,1:27:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有，那个可怜的家伙\N{\rENG}Yeah, I did, that poor bastard.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:29.16,1:27:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以困住她 防火门在底层出口打开了\N{\rENG}We can trap her. The fire door opens from the inside at the bottom exit.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:34.12,1:27:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后怎样？\N{\rENG}Then what?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:37.50,1:27:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他妈的\N{\rENG}Holy shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:38.92,1:27:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 哦，上帝  - 那婊子穿过了钢门\N{\rENG}- Oh, my God. - The bitch went through a steel door!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:42.38,1:27:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,菲奇！丹！我们在停车场！ 她溜掉了！\N{\rENG}Fitch! Dan! We're in the garage! She got past us!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:56.56,1:27:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你见到她？ - 她在我们到达前已离开\N{\rENG}- You saw her? - She was gone before we got here.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:59.27,1:28:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 来  - 你见到她！\N{\rENG}- Here. - You saw her!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:01.19,1:28:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 看看那扇门！ - 她去哪儿了？\N{\rENG}- Look at the door! - Which way did she go?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:03.40,1:28:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 普雷斯顿呢？ - 到了隧道下面！\N{\rENG}- Where's Press? - He took off down that tunnel.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:20.79,1:28:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她感到受威胁时就会杀人\N{\rENG}She kills if she feels threatened. She kills if she feels threatened.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:48.44,1:28:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她一定曾经过这儿\N{\rENG}She must've come through here.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:12.88,1:29:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她曾下来这里\N{\rENG}She went down here. There's no other way.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:15.10,1:29:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对，她曾在这下面\N{\rENG}Yeah, she's down there.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:17.81,1:29:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧\N{\rENG}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:19.56,1:29:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,退后，我去清除一下\N{\rENG}Stand back, I'll clear it out.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:15.11,1:30:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她朝哪个方向，丹？\N{\rENG}Which way did she go, Dan?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:18.53,1:30:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我不知道  - 什么？\N{\rENG}- I don't know. - What?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:20.70,1:30:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不确定\N{\rENG}I'm not sure. She's here.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:22.87,1:30:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想一想！你是有超感官的能力！ 那个方向？\N{\rENG}Think. You're supposed to have some extrasensory power! Which way?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:28.59,1:30:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 她去了哪个方向？ - 我不知道！\N{\rENG}- Which way did she go, Dan? - I don't know! I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:36.01,1:30:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 那边  - 这已经足够了\N{\rENG}- I think she went that way. - That's good enough for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:39.01,1:30:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你认为她往那边走？\N{\rENG}You think she went that way?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:42.14,1:30:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你什么也不知道的，不是吗？\N{\rENG}You don't fucking know, don't you? You don't fucking know.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:45.02,1:30:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我往这边走，跟我来\N{\rENG}I'll go this way. You come with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:47.65,1:30:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 丹，跟我来！ - 菲奇\N{\rENG}- Come with me, Dan! - Fitch.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:51.52,1:30:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我认为她往这边走了\N{\rENG}I think she went this way.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:11.13,1:31:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丹？\N{\rENG}Dan?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:16.05,1:31:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丹？\N{\rENG}Dan?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:54.63,1:31:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,菲奇\N{\rENG}Fitch. Fitch.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:57.42,1:31:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丹？\N{\rENG}Dan?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:01.47,1:32:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？\N{\rENG}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:12.11,1:32:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以感觉到她\N{\rENG}I can feel her.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:14.11,1:32:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她在那一边\N{\rENG}She's that way.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:16.19,1:32:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她在那一边\N{\rENG}She's that way.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:21.78,1:32:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我从没想过要杀人的\N{\rENG}I never thought I'd want to kill something.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:24.83,1:32:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也没想过\N{\rENG}Never thought I'd want to.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:01.91,1:33:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是这边 在这里后面\N{\rENG}It's this way. It's back here.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:36.06,1:33:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她在里面\N{\rENG}Hey, she went in here.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:43.53,1:33:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是在地震时给震开的\N{\rENG}This must have opened up during the earthquake.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:47.28,1:33:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们退后\N{\rENG}Okay, stand back.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:05.07,1:35:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是油吗？\N{\rENG}Is that oil?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:06.57,1:35:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像是\N{\rENG}Looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:15.58,1:35:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回去看看能否把她冲出来\N{\rENG}I'm going back there to see if I can flush her out.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:18.96,1:35:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若她穿过这儿回来，便攻击她\N{\rENG}If she comes back through here, let her have it.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:37.06,1:35:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丹\N{\rENG}Dan. Dan!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:38.71,1:36:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 那是什么？ - 我不知道\N{\rENG}- Dan, what is it?  - I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:42.04,1:36:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道\N{\rENG}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:44.10,1:37:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丹\N{\rENG}Dan.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:06.88,1:38:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事\N{\rENG}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:10.38,1:38:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事的\N{\rENG}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:13.30,1:38:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有人会伤害你\N{\rENG}Nobody's gonna hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:15.43,1:38:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过来\N{\rENG}You come here.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:18.97,1:38:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过来，我扶你\N{\rENG}Come on. I got you.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:26.02,1:38:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丹出事了！\N{\rENG}Press, something's happened to Dan!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:29.36,1:38:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事吗？\N{\rENG}You okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:33.74,1:38:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕\N{\rENG}Shit!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:37.20,1:38:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丹？\N{\rENG}Dan?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:39.70,1:38:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丹？\N{\rENG}Dan?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:42.20,1:38:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我被困了！\N{\rENG}I'm stuck!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:48.58,1:38:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帮帮我！我被困住了！\N{\rENG}I need your help! I'm stuck!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:20.20,1:39:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丹，撑着点！\N{\rENG}Dan, you gotta hang on!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:29.50,1:39:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,普雷斯顿\N{\rENG}Press!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:35.26,1:39:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,撑着点，丹\N{\rENG}Dan, keep on.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:50.65,1:39:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,普雷斯顿\N{\rENG}Press!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:43.12,1:40:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,撑着点！\N{\rENG}Hang on, Dan!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:46.74,1:40:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,撑着点\N{\rENG}Hang on!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:49.33,1:40:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我抓住你了\N{\rENG}I got you.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:52.08,1:40:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我抓住你了\N{\rENG}I got you, Dan. Hang on.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:54.79,1:40:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕\N{\rENG}Shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:03.76,1:41:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,撑着点\N{\rENG}Hang on!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:07.31,1:41:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丹，撑着点\N{\rENG}Hang on, Dan!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:12.77,1:41:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除掉她！\N{\rENG}Get rid of her, Press!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:19.19,1:41:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,低头\N{\rENG}Duck your head.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:21.99,1:41:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去你的，死吧\N{\rENG}Let go, you motherfucker.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:26.87,1:41:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我抓住你了  - 糟糕\N{\rENG}- I got you. Hold on, I got you. - Shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:35.17,1:41:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为会没命\N{\rENG}I thought I was dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:40.30,1:41:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以为你再没机会喝长岛冰茶了\N{\rENG}I thought you'd drank your last Long Island Ice Tea.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:43.68,1:41:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以为大家都是\N{\rENG}Yeah, I thought we all had.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:47.43,1:41:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吗？\N{\rENG}Hey, you okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:50.14,1:41:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事\N{\rENG}Yeah, I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:52.56,1:41:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的裤子很邋遢\N{\rENG}My pants are a little messed up.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:55.06,1:41:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过我没事\N{\rENG}But I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:58.82,1:42:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是半人半怪物\N{\rENG}She was half us, half something else.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:02.15,1:42:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道哪边才是掠食性的\N{\rENG}I wonder which was the predatory half.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:05.66,1:42:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那死了的一边\N{\rENG}The dead half.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:07.58,1:42:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们走吧\N{\rENG}Let's get the hell out of here.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:53.58,1:42:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没想过回到水渠来 会这么开心的\N{\rENG}I never thought I'd be so happy to be back in a sewer.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:12.58,1:43:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,浮氺印
Dialogue: 0,1:43:16.58,1:43:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢观赏


